refuseTemplates.reply:
Hello, your suggestion has been refused because it already has been suggested and viewed by the bot owner.
Have a nice day ^^

refuseTemplates.label: Invalid beats type
refuseTemplates.value: You can't put automatically the beats type
refuseTemplates.reply:
Hello, your suggestion can't be added because the beats type (something like "lofi hip hop/relaxing beats" in the title) can't be added.
Thank you for submitting this suggestion, maybe my owner will add it manually.
Have a cool day !

refuseTemplates.label: Too short
refuseTemplates.value: The music playlist is too short to be added
refuseTemplates.reply:
Hello, you've suggested a music to add it in my songs, unfortunately, I think that this music is too short to be added.
You always can try to resubmit it, maybe my owner will accept it.
I hope you to have a good day !
